Class
Description

The AdminController class handles the requests and manages the operations related to the admin functionality in the application.

The HomeController class is a Spring MVC controller responsible for handling various requests related to the home page, user login, admin login, doctor login, user registration, and other related functionalities.

Interface for the user service.
